      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 configuration (5.5 mm rod, straight trajectory). Clinical use includes variable rod diameters and screw angulations not covered by this validation. Achieved level falls one gradation below required level; this gap is acknowledged and carried forward as a known limitation of the validation scope."
