    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) reflects the use of a single ASTM F1717 loading configuration and does not invalidate the validation for the specific COU, which is also limited to that configuration. All three quantitative QoI acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96 and <10% difference) are satisfied. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the Medium assurance level required for this Class II device submission.",
